OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779678251
OL,3,CShop numbers return to growth after
OL,4,Cyears of decline, say experts
OL,6,FUK high streets and shopping
OL,7,Fdestinations are showing signs of
OL,8,Frecovery as more than 13 retail stores
OL,9,Fopened each week over the past year,
OL,10,Faccording to new figures.
OL,12,FHowever, England and Wales have still
OL,13,Fseen more than 6,000 retail premises
OL,14,Fvanish from local communities over the
OL,15,Fpast five years.
OL,17,FAnalysis of Valuation Office Agency
OL,18,Fdata by tax firm Ryan, found that
OL,19,Fthere were 507,810 retail premises
OL,20,Facross England and Wales at the end of
OL,21,F2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
