FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779678251
OL,3,CShop numbers return to growth after
OL,4,Cyears of decline, say experts
OL,6,FIt said the figures showed that a
OL,7,Frecent contraction across the sector
OL,8,Fhas appeared to stabilise, with a 723
OL,9,Fnet increase in the number of retail
OL,10,Fstores compared with a year earlier.
OL,12,FProperty numbers increased across
OL,13,Fevery region of England and Wales,
OL,14,Fwith the exception of the North West,
OL,15,Fwhich saw a decline of 41.
OL,17,FIt suggests that parts of the sector
OL,18,Fare now beginning to rebalance
OL,19,Ffollowing significant structural
OL,20,Fcontraction seen since the pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
