OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779678251
OL,3,CShop numbers return to growth after
OL,4,Cyears of decline, say experts
OL,6,FThe creation of new retail units also
OL,7,Fcomes as many retail real estate
OL,8,Ffirms, such as Hammerson, have turned
OL,9,Fempty large units, often former
OL,10,Fdepartment stores, into a greater
OL,11,Fnumber of smaller units.
OL,13,FOther retail groups, such as John
OL,14,FLewis, have moved away from ambitions
OL,15,Fto transform some retail property for
OL,16,Fother uses such as rental
OL,17,Faccommodation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
