OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779678251
OL,3,CShop numbers return to growth after
OL,4,Cyears of decline, say experts
OL,6,FNevertheless, the retail sector is
OL,7,Fstill facing pressure from higher
OL,8,Fbusiness rates for many firms,
OL,9,Fincreased labour costs and concerns
OL,10,Fover consumer sentiment.
OL,12,FThe data also shows that there has
OL,13,Falso been significant decline over the
OL,14,Fpast few years, with a net reduction
OL,15,Fof 6,045 retail properties since the
OL,16,Fend of 2020.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
