OL,3,CShop numbers return to growth after
OL,4,Cyears of decline, say experts
OL,6,FLondon recorded the largest five-year
OL,7,Fregional reduction, with 1,266 retail
OL,8,Fpremises disappearing over the period,
OL,9,Ffollowed by the South East (-1,191),
OL,10,FNorth West (-719) and North East (-
OL,11,F672).
OL,13,FThe figures show retail premises which
OL,14,Fhave permanently disappeared from
OL,15,Fcommunities altogether, having either
OL,16,Fbeen demolished or converted for
OL,17,Falternative use.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
