OL,3,CShop numbers return to growth after
OL,4,Cyears of decline, say experts
OL,6,FThe figures come as Ryan's 2026 annual
OL,7,Fbusiness rates review highlighted that
OL,8,Fthe retail sector saw a 9.3% increase
OL,9,Fin rateable values at the 2026
OL,10,Fbusiness rates revaluation despite the
OL,11,Fmajor shift in the retail landscape
OL,12,Fsince the pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
