OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779678251
OL,3,CShop numbers return to growth after
OL,4,Cyears of decline, say experts
OL,6,FAlex Probyn, practice leader for
OL,7,FEurope and Asia-Pacific property tax
OL,8,Fat Ryan, said: "The pandemic
OL,9,Faccelerated structural changes that
OL,10,Fwere already emerging across the
OL,11,Fretail sector, including changing
OL,12,Fconsumer behaviour, hybrid working
OL,13,Fpatterns and a reduced reliance on
OL,14,Ftraditional retail floorspace in many
OL,15,Flocations.
OL,26,@pD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
