PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779678251
OL,3,CShop numbers return to growth after
OL,4,Cyears of decline, say experts
OL,6,F"Many locations were arguably over-
OL,7,Fretailed before Covid and high streets
OL,8,Fhave evolved towards more mixed-use
OL,9,Fenvironments, with retail space being
OL,10,Frebalanced alongside growing demand
OL,11,Ffor residential, leisure, hospitality
OL,12,Fand service-led uses.
OL,14,F"The revaluation outcome does suggest
OL,15,Fa large proportion of retail premises
OL,16,Fhave seen bigger increases in their
OL,17,Fassessments than underlying market
OL,18,Fconditions and rental evidence would
OL,19,Fhave led occupiers to expect.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
